        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Make the dough",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Combine the flour, sugar, salt, and yeast. Add the milk, eggs, egg yolk, and vanilla and mix to a shaggy dough. Knead for 8 minutes. Add the softened butter in additions and continue kneading until the dough is smooth and passes the window-pane test, about 8 more minutes. The dough will be soft. Prove in an oiled bowl for 1 to 1.5 hours until doubled.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Shape and prove",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "On a lightly floured surface, roll the proved dough to 1.5 cm thick. Cut into rounds using a 7 cm cutter. Place on baking-paper squares on trays, cover loosely, and prove for 45 to 60 minutes until puffed and light.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Fry and fill",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Heat the oil to 170°C. Slide 3 sufganiyot at a time into the oil using the baking-paper squares. Fry for 2 minutes per side until deep amber. Drain on a rack. While still warm, insert a thin nozzle into the side of each and pipe in about 20 g of strained jam. Dust generously with icing sugar and serve within 2 hours.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
